author: Kynix @KynixXBT
text: Notice how $BTC went below 90k and BTC.dominance fell with it. I called the top at 64% for Btc.d. And I think it will keep going down at least till 54% with further targets 50% and 46%. This also means once BTC bottoms, which should be here, Altcoins will perform quite good.
